headline: Warby Parker Stock Pops on Partnership With Google to Develop AI Glasses
summary: Warby Parker is working with Google to develop glasses that will rival an offering from Meta Platforms.  Google said at its keynote on Tuesday that Warby Parker was one of two companies that "will be the first eyewear partners to build glasses with Android XR."  Warby Parker said in a news release on Tuesday that it is partnering with Google to develop AI-powered glasses "intended for all-day wear."
